      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version-controlled release with documented test suite; all simulation scripts must be archived with checksums.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under a validated release managed by the institution's HPC software governance process. Simulation case files, UDF source code, and post-processing scripts are archived in a Git repository with SHA-256 checksums. The solver test suite covers all physics models activated in this study. SQA level 2 requirements are fully satisfied."
    },
    {
