      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor; default level 1 acceptance applies.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit characterisation of iterative solver error beyond residual convergence monitoring is not required. Residuals were converged to 1e-5 for all equations in all production runs. No further assessment is warranted."
    },
    {
